{
  "stem": "2539.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father lived in a house near to the railway station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I could have gone there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I forgot that he was there, because I was involved in a conversation with him and we were talking, two young children talking together.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was going by foot to Olyka.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I went with him to Olyka and he helped me to carry my suitcase.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this was a few days before the Germans entered Olyka-- a few days before the Germans entered Olyka.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When they entered Olyka, oh, [SIGHS] there were two spies walking along our house, along the street, and I knew that they didn't belong there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I ran into the-- ran into the house and said, Mama, there are-- there are two spies here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They don't belong.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were looking at the houses and peeping their heads into-- because they were going-- the following day, they bombed Olyka.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there were two German spies on a-- what's the word for it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were doing a-- in Polish, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were-- Like a rickey?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Reconnaissance.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were sort of--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Surveying.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Surveying.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the following day, the bombs came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And really, you know, the bomb fell in the house next door and it hit an old woman who was distantly related-- I don't know how-- and she-- she got-- she got killed.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is where I had my first, and only, thank God, I think, near-death experience.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was very young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were like sardines under the house in the cellar--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In hiding when the-- when they were bombing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the bomb fell next door that felt as if it was falling on us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was a real near-death experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I thought this was really the end.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
